 det \u00e5 gj\u00f8re vesentlige endringer i l\u00f8pet av en kontraktsperiode, er sv\u00e6rt dyrt, sier Karin Bj\u00f8rkhaug, leder i samferdselskomiteen, Karin Bj\u00f8rkhaug (Krf)."]}, {"field": "category0", "value": "nyheter"}, {"field": "category1", "value": "nyheter|sortrondelag"}, {"field": "contenthash", "value": "cd82269f32e188272e8ef834a761698ad731cd7418379af9c0a4ce8f716eaf03"}, {"field": "createtime", "value": "2016-06-25T01:55:01.000Z"}, {"field": "description", "value": "Bilister fortviler over ferjetilbudet mellom Brekstad og Valset, mens fylkesordf\u00f8reren mener flere m\u00e5 ta i bruk andre veier."}, {"field": "dominantimage", "value": "http://www.adressa.no/incoming/article11234787.ece/zcc6jh/ALTERNATES/w980-default/valset2.jpg"}, {"field": "dominantimagedimensions", "value": "980x551"}, {"field": "dominantthumbnail", "value": "http://content-thumbnail.cxpublic.com/content/dominantthumbnail/822af7489217a022333ce401e4a212fa73b72d2a.jpg?5988644f"}, {"field": "dominantthumbnaildimensions", "value": "300x169"}, {"field": "heading", "value": ["- Flere enn n\u00f8dvendig kj\u00f8rer Brekstad", "D\u00e5rlige toalettforhold", "M\u00f8tte fylkesordf\u00f8reren", "Mest penger til \u00d8rland", "Utfordrer Norled", "Styrker ikke tilbudet", "Fosen-strategi"]}, {"field": "id", "value": "822af7489217a022333ce401e4a212fa73b72d2a"}, {"field": "keyword", "value": ["utenriks", "innenriks", "trondheim", "E6", "midtbyen", "bybrann", "bilulykker"]}, {"field": "keywords", "value": "utenriks,innenriks,trondheim,E6,midtbyen,bybrann,bilulykker"}, {"field": "kw-category", "value": ["nyheter", "sortrondelag"]}, {"field": "kw-classification", "value": "law-government-and-politics"}, {"field": "kw-company", "value": "facebook"}, {"field": "kw-concept", "value": ["ferja t\u00e5ler", "styrke tilbudet", "\u00f8kt", "ferje", "kapasitet", "samband", "tilbudet", "krevende samband", "minste ferja t\u00e5ler", "minste ferja"]}, {"field": "kw-entity", "value": ["fosen", "valset", "br